{
  "texts": [
    "It has never been more critical to address the potential harms associated with LLMs [63].",
    "Social prompt engineering presents interesting opportunities and challenges for responsible AI.",
    "On the one hand, social systems like Wordflow can enable users to share prompting techniques [8] to mitigate potential harms.",
    "On the other hand, without content moderation, users can easily disseminate harmful prompts, such as a misinformation generator [26].",
    "In Wordflow, users can report harmful prompts, and we will diligently monitor and moderate community prompts."
  ]
}